Getting Started with Ice

Installing Ice on Linux

	cd /etc/yum.repos.d 
	wget https://zeroc.com/download/Ice/3.7/el7/zeroc-ice3.7.repo

	yum makecache fast 

	yum install ice-all-runtime ice-all-devel

Setting Up you Linux Environment to Ice
	
	c++ -c -DICE_CPP11_MAPPING -pthread myprogram.cpp 

































































































































































































































